quran[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,"Si ko darotoongal ngal dariima,"
  56,2,"alanaa daragol maggal ngol pennoowo."
  56,3,"Koyfin…óinatngal (yeddu…ďe), …ďamtatngal (goo…óii…ďe)."
  56,4,"Si lesdi ndiin dilliniraama dillannde,"
  56,5,"pelle …óeen munciroyee muncannde,"
  56,6,"…óe ngonta collaari ruuynatndi,"
  56,7,"Mbattinon nooneeji tati :"
  56,8,"Ko wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďeen - iskin …ďeen yim…ďe √Īaamo !"
  56,9,"e wontiroo…ďe nano …ďeen, bis e …ďeen yim…ďe nano !"
  56,10,"Ko adondiratnoo…ďe …ďeen (e mo∆ī∆īere ka aduna), adoytee (naatneede Aljanna)."
  56,11,"Ko …ďeen ngoni badnitaa…ďe …ďeen."
  56,12,"ka Aljannaaji ne'eminii…ói,"
  56,13,"dental jeyaangal e [mofte] adinoo…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,14,"e see…óaa…ďe jiyaa…ďe e [mofte] sakkitii…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,15,"he…ďe e hoore dan…óe yu…ď…ďiraa…óe [kaŇčŇče],"
  56,16,"hara he…ďe so…ď…ďindii e majje, feewtondir…ďe."
  56,17,"Sukaa…ďe duuminaa…ďe hino mbanngoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe,"
  56,18,"wonndude e √Īeddu…óe, e cataloy, e koroy e [hebbiniraakoy] beere ilatnde,"
  56,19,"…ďe muusetaake ko*e ndeer toon, …ďe ciwritaa;"
  56,20,"e muuyantee…ói …ói …ďe cu…ďotoo,"
  56,21,"E teewu colli ngu …ďe tuuyatee."
  56,22,"E huurul'aynii…ďe -yaaja gite en …ďeen."
  56,23,"nanndu…ďe e kaŇčŇče lu'lu'u maraa…óe;(coomaa…óe)."
  56,24,"njo…ďdi ko …ďe ngollatnoo koon."
  56,25,"∆Āe nanataa ndeer ton haala mhere, wonaa ko bakkondiŇčta;"
  56,26,"si wonaa wi'aneede : ""Salaaman! Salaaman!"" [Sa…ói mon! sa…ói mon!]."
  56,27,"E wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďeen, ko ngoni …ďeen yim…ďe √Īaamo?"
  56,28,"[∆Āe ngonat] e le…ó…óe jaa…ďe neew…óu…óe,"
  56,29,"E banaanaje pawandir…óe."
  56,30,"E …óowdi duumiindi,"
  56,31,"E ndiyam juurat…óam,"
  56,32,"e …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe …óuu…óu…óe"
  56,33,"…óe ta∆īondirtaa …óe ka…óetaake."
  56,34,"E dan…óe …ďamtaa…óe."
  56,35,"Ko minen tagi pu…ó…ói …ďe (pu…ó…óagol)."
  56,36,"Min mba…ói …ďe curbaa…ďe-boomi-."
  56,37,"yi…óu…ďe wor…ďe mum, goree…ďe."
  56,38,"[Min marani …ďe] yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďeen."
  56,39,"Dental jiyaa…ďe e [mofte] adinoo…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,40,"E see…óaa…ďe jiyaa…ďe e [mofte] sakkitii…ďe …ďeen."
  56,41,"E wontiroo…ďe nano …ďeen. Ko hom…ďe nhoni …ďeen yim…ďe nano?"
  56,42,"[∆Āeen] no e nguleendi e patat…óam,"
  56,43,"E …óowdi curki …ďawluki,"
  56,44,"wonaa …ďuu…ďndi, wonaa teddundi."
  56,45,"Ado …óuum, hari ko …ďe neeminaa…ďe."
  56,46,"…ďe laatino he…ďe deppitoo e bakkaat maw…ói …óiin,"
  56,47,"he…ďe mbi'atnoo: ""Enee, si min maayii, min ngontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, hara ko min immintinoytee…ďe?"
  56,48,"hay baabiraa…ďe amen adinoo…ďe …ďeen?"""
  56,49,"Maaku : ""pellet, aram…ďe e sakkitii…ďe …ďe."
  56,50,"ko moo…ďoytee…ďe e √Īalaande anndaande waktu mum."
  56,51,"refti pellet, onon …ďee majju…ďe yeddu…ďe [ummital],"
  56,52,"ko on √Īaamoyay…ďe e leggal ""Zaqquumi"" ngal"
  56,53,"kebbiniron ngal deedi,"
  56,54,"njariron ngal kadi patat…óam,"
  56,55,"Njariron wa jargol ngelooba …óom…óaamba""."
  56,56,"Ko …óuum woni ko …ďe kottiigu !u! en √Īalnde njo…ďdi diina."
  56,57,"Ko Minen ngoni ko tagi on. Ha…ói ngooŇč…óion [Min immintinat on]?"
  56,58,"On nj'ii on maniiyu mo ndufoton?"
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata mo? Kaa ko minen ngoni tagoo…ďe […óum]?"
  56,60,"Ko Minen koddiri maayde ndeen hakkunde mon. Min ngonaani adatee…ďe"
  56,61,"E battitugol yeruu…ďe mon, Min pu…ó…óira on e ko on ngannda."
  56,62,"GooŇč…óii ho…óon nganndi tageede aranun …óum. Ko ha…ói mbaajito…óon?"
  56,63,"On nji'ii ko ko ndemoton?"
  56,64,"Ko onon pu…óinta …óum? Kaa ko Minen ngoni fu…óinoo…ďe …ďeen?"
  56,65,"Si min kaajuno, pellet, Min mba…óayno ndu foron. Mbattinon hi…óon kaawoo [mbi'a] :"
  56,66,"""Minen ko min leptetee…ďe perte ko min nafqi ko."
  56,67,"wurin ko min ha…óaa…ďe!""."
  56,68,"On yi'ii ndiyam …óam njaroton …óam?"
  56,69,"E ko onon njippiniri …óam ka duule? Kaa ko minen njippini […óam]?"
  56,70,"Si Min kaajuno, Min mba…óayno …óam kaa…ó…óam. Ko ha…ói njetton [Allah]?"
  56,71,"On nj'ii yiite nge ku…ď…ďoton ngen?"
  56,72,"E ko onon woodini wa…ói le…ó…óe mum? Kaa ko Minen ngoodini […óe]?"
  56,73,"Min mba…óir ngen [yiite] waaju, e nafitor nge setotoo…ďe."
  56,74,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, maw…óo oon!"
  56,75,"Mi woo…óndirii mutir…óe koode …óeen."
  56,76,"Pellet, …óuum ko woondoore mawnde, si ho…óon nganndunoo."
  56,77,"Pellet nee ko alqur'aanaare konde teddunde,"
  56,78,"won'de e deftere reenaande"
  56,79,"meemataa nden si wonaa la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďeen;"
  56,80,"ko jippiniraande ka Jey…óo winndere ndeen."
  56,81,"E ko ndee yeewtere woŇčki ko njeddoton onon?"
  56,82,"Ho…óon mba…óa arsike mon (to…ďo ngon) ko on yeddoo…ďe [arsiku…óo On]?"
  56,83,"Ko ha…óata nde woŇčkii yottii ka looko∆īere,"
  56,84,"hara onon ho…óon ndaara on tumba,"
  56,85,"hara non ko Minen …ďuri on …ďadaade mo, kono on nji'ataa."
  56,86,"Ko ha…óata on, si tawiino on njo…ďetaake."
  56,87,"Ndutton kin [woŇčkii], si tawii ko on goongu…ďe?"
  56,88,"Si tawii on ko jiyaa…óo e …ďattinaa…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,89,"haray ko foftere, e mo∆ī∆īere, e Aljannaaji ne'ema (woodani mo)."
  56,90,"Si tawii kadi ko jiyaa…óo e yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďeen,"
  56,91,"haray [o ja…ď…ďoroyte] : ""Kisal maa"" e …ďaŇčge yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďeen."
  56,92,"Si tawii noon ko jiyanoo…óo e yeddu…ďe majju…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,93,"haray ho…ótorde makko on ko patay…óam,"
  56,94,"E sumeede Jahiimi."
  56,95,"Pellet, ko …óum woni goonga jananaa…óo oon."
  56,96,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, maw…óo oon!"
